creator: weeyu
descriptionHtml:
The APP is connected to the charging pile via WiFi for data interaction.
It has the charging stop control of the charging pile and the setting of the charging method. You can remotely view the status of the charging pile and real-time data of the charging process.And it has the functions of viewing historical records, charging order statistics and so on.
descriptionShort: WE E-Charge is a mobile phone APP for managing specific smart charging piles.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
WE E-Charge是一个款用于管理特定智能充电桩的手机APP。
该APP通过wifi与充电桩连接，进行数据交互。
具备对充电桩的充电启停控制，以及充电方式的设置，
可方便远程看到充电桩状态以及充电过程实时数据。
并且具有查看历史充电记录，充电订单统计等功能。
